### Problem Analysis:
Java side shows `account [TB16q6kpSEW2WqvTJ9ua7HAoP9ugQ2HdHZ] does not exist` error, while Rust side successfully executes transactions and logs show account access attempts. This indicates a state synchronization gap between Rust execution and Java database.

### Error Pattern:
```
ERROR [sync-handle-block] [DB](Manager.java:1367) account [TB16q6kpSEW2WqvTJ9ua7HAoP9ugQ2HdHZ] does not exist
